<package name="falco-libs" project="openSUSE:Factory">
  <title>Libraries for system inspection (libscap and libsinsp)</title>
  <description>The falcosecurity libs are the core libraries behind Falco and sysdig:
libscap (system capture) reads kernel events from the various drivers and
capture files; libsinsp (system inspection) provides the state engine,
filtering, event formatting and plugin framework on top of libscap.</description>
  <url>https://github.com/falcosecurity/libs</url>
</package>
